body:
### Welcome to Feeney Welding and Fence, a Stayshine Developers Project


### Authors and Contributors
Mark Grover (@)
Michael Rosata(@mrosata)

### Support or Contact
Get here on accident? Looking for help designing web applications or finding your way home? We can help, and all you have to do is [click here for Stayshine.com](http://stayshine.com) or if you are part of the project and want to get home, [click here for the Stayshine YouTrack Page on JetBrains](http://stayshine.myjetbrains.com).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
